Royal Palm Beach Seafood Festival
Saturday & Sunday March 15th & 16th
Commons Park
11600 Poinciana Blvd., Royal Palm Beach, FL
​
FREE Admission & FREE Parking
Event Hours:​
​
Saturday
11am to 8pm & Sunday 11am to 6pm
​​
​
​
T
he Royal Palm Beach Seafood Festival
will offer an abundance of
Delicious Seafood,
Back-to-Back Entertainment on 2 Stages
and
Vendors from Coast to Coast!
We invite you to join us for some of the freshest Seafood in South Florida
and to enjoy a diverse variety of delectable dishes and tasty libations.
​
Fear not ye landlubbers, thar will also be plenty of non-seafood menu selections to choose from.
​​
The Royal Palm Beach Seafood Festival will also play host to some great live entertainment.
There will be Pirates & Mermaids, a Free Kids’ Fun Zone, interesting exhibits & displays along with a nice assortment of Vendors to shop and explore!
​PLENTY OF FREE ON-SITE PARKING
​
​
Personal Tents
and
​
Large Umbrellas
are Not Permitted within the Seafood Festival.
Entertainment, Performers, Attractions, Scheduling and Food selections are subject to change without notice.
Food and Beverage is not included with free admission but is available for purchase.
Consuming raw or under cooked meats, poultry, seafood, shellfish or eggs may increase your risk of foodborne illness.

Well behaved pets on a leash and responsible pet owners are always welcome at our events.
Folding chairs and blankets are allowed.
